  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an open label, multicenter, single-arm phase II trial with primary
      eqirubicine-oxaliplatin-capecitabine chemotherapy and concurrent Pmab in patients with
      resectable, histologically proven gastric or esophageal cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
